  "description": "Okay, I\u0026rsquo;ve successfully gotten back into Obsidian, and I\u0026rsquo;ve managed to get Quartz working well enough. (\u0026ldquo;Managed to get\u0026rdquo; makes it sound harder than it was - I\u0026rsquo;m just very out of practice with really using my computer for more than clicking on things or dumping into a text interface.)\nI\u0026rsquo;m keen to set up some kind of routine for bringing in older content, but I think for now, it\u0026rsquo;s just about set-up enough for me to actually replace the older version of emsenn.net that\u0026rsquo;s live now. I checked earlier today, and there\u0026rsquo;s actually not that much content up there.\n",
